Ultralite2
==========

The second generation core framework for Pixelpost.

Requirements
------------

* PHP 5.2
* SQLite or mySQL

Setup & Configuration
---------------------

1. Modify and rename `sample_htaccess` to `.htaccess`.
2. Adjust the settings in `application/config.php`.

